text.section:
In making grants under this subtitle, the Trust shall give consideration to:
The amount of funds contributed to the project by the land trust as a match against the grant;
The amount of funds contributed to the project by parties other than the land trust or the Trust;
The natural resource, open space, or recreational value of the project;
Geographic distribution;
The degree of development pressure in the area; and
Whether the grant will be reimbursed to the Land Trust Grant Fund, as provided by § 3-2A-08 of this subtitle.
